[04:49] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'more than that. It is a logic system the likes of which we can\'t really define because the only other system we\'re familiar with is our own brains. So, yes, we might be looking at a mirror. Yes, we might be trying to build a mind.'

[05:02] [scene:talk]
