VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the US if you are an adult and not a child. So, it\'s already here. If you use AI now, and I can\'t imagine you don\'t because you\'re probably using Google. It\'s been incorporated into everything.'

[05:42] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'You probably see the issues that it has. So, one thing that we can do to improve these systems is give them context so they know what failure modes they have and they know how to improve things down the line. They need to be able to sort their memories and self-improve, which'

